This is just a waste of time.} 6. Nxf3 Nh5 7. d4 f6 $2 {With White's Queen on
e2, Black cannot afford to play either ...d6 or ...f6 because he cannot keep
his own Queen on the "hot" file to shield his King.} 8. Nd5 Qd8 9. exf6+ Kf7
10. Ng5+ Kg8 {Allowing an amusing finish.} (10... Kg6 11. Qe4+ Kh6 12. Nf7#)
11. f7# 1-0

