1. e4 e5 2. Nc3 Nf6 3. f4 Nc6 4. fxe5 Nxe5 5. d4 Ng6 6. e5 Ng8 7. Nf3 Bb4 8.
Bc4 h6 $2 9. O-O Bxc3 10. bxc3 {Now White threatens 11.Ng5 anyway, since
Black's Knight on g6 will fall to the fork at f7.} 10... f6 (10... d5 {
is the only hope, though after} 11. exd6 Qxd6 12. Qe2+ N8e7 (12... Qe7 13.
Bxf7+ $1 Kxf7 14. Ne5+ Ke8 15. Qh5 $1 $18) 13. Ne5 Nxe5 14. dxe5 {
Black is lost:} 14... Qc5+ 15. Be3 Qxe5 16. Bxf7+ Kf8 17. Qd3 $18 {etc.}) 11.
Nh4 (11. exf6 Nxf6 12. Ne5 (12. Re1+ Kf8 13. Ne5 Nxe5 14. dxe5 Ng8 15. Rf1+ Ke8
16. Qh5+ g6 17. Qxg6+ Ke7) 12... Nxe5 13. dxe5 $18) 11... Nxh4 12. Qh5+ Kf8 $4
(12... g6 13. Qxh4 $18) 13. Qf7# 1-0

